STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Julie Ann BREEDING, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1478 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Julie Ann Breeding appeals following her convictions for possession of methamphetamine with intent to deliver and failure to possess a drug tax stamp as a second or subsequent offender. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
